&lt;h1 id="the-modern-struggle-is-fighting-weaponized-addiction"&gt;The Modern Struggle Is Fighting Weaponized Addiction&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 24 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
On some very deep level, all pleasure creates its own offsetting pain and fear of loss. I recently tweeted, &amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;In an age of abundance, pursuing pleasure for its own sake creates addiction.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rdquo; I was upgrading a &lt;strong&gt;Miyamoto Musashi&lt;/strong&gt; line, &amp;ldquo;Do not seek pleasure for its own sake.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>